Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我点提示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“人形”的弱点是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上的环
